# [Your Project Name] — CLAUDE.md

## Production methodology
See `~/.claude/methodology/production-pipeline.md`. This project runs under Solo Studio.
- EP chat: cross-sprint, defines scope, never writes code
- Owner chat: one per sprint, coordinates workers, merges branches
- Worker chats: EP-authorised only, each in its own git worktree

